<para style="p">For the chief musician. A psalm of David; when Nathan the prophet came to him after he had slept with Bathsheba.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Have mercy on me, God, because of your covenant faithfulness;</para>

<para style="q1">for the sake of the multitude of your merciful actions, blot out my transgressions.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Wash me thoroughly from my iniquity</para>

<para style="q1">and cleanse me from my sin.</para>
